OL,6,FA couple from Oxfordshire, who lost
OL,7,Ftheir life savings in an investment
OL,8,Fscam, say they were confident they had
OL,9,Fmade all the necessary checks.
OL,11,FMarilyn Hamblin and her husband Gareth
OL,12,Fhave been trying to get to the bottom
OL,13,Fof what happened to their money.
OL,15,FSix years ago they were looking for
OL,16,Fsomewhere to put their savings to try
OL,17,Fto increase their pension pot.
OL,19,FThey did some online research and
OL,20,Ffound a company offering investments
OL,21,Fin commodities and currencies.
