OL,6,FMarilyn said they were careful and
OL,7,FGareth travelled to London to meet
OL,8,Fwith a company representative before
OL,9,Fthey parted with any money.
OL,11,FBut after investing around #300,000 it
OL,12,Fbecame clear the company was
OL,13,Ffraudulent.
OL,15,FThe company stopped answering calls,
OL,16,Fthe website disappeared and the
OL,17,Fcouple's money had gone.
