OL,6,FAfter a police investigation Jonathan
OL,7,FArafiena pleaded guilty to one count
OL,8,Fof money laundering and conspiracy to
OL,9,Fdefraud at Southwark Crown Court.
OL,11,FHe is now serving a five year sentence.
OL,13,FCity of London Police said Arafiena
OL,14,Fran a 'boiler room' - a term given to
OL,15,Ffraud carried on by means of distance
OL,16,Fselling and telesales.
