OL,6,FVictims are pressurised into buying
OL,7,Fproducts or investments on a false
OL,8,Fpremise, which historically used to
OL,9,Ftake place in basements or boiler
OL,10,Frooms.
OL,12,FThe Hamblins were not the only
OL,13,Fvictims, with police estimating that
OL,14,Fover #12m was taken from hundreds of
OL,15,Fpeople over a two-and-a-half-year
OL,16,Fperiod.
