OL,6,FDetective Inspector Gareth Dothie,
OL,7,Ffrom the Fraud Operations team at the
OL,8,FCity of London Police, said: "Arafiena
OL,9,Fled an extravagant lifestyle where he
OL,10,Fpurchased high-end cars, luxury
OL,11,Fwatches and gold bullion from the
OL,12,Fproceeds of criminal activity.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately for him, we seized all
OL,14,Fof these and he is now facing a
OL,15,Flengthy sentence behind bars."
OL,17,FGareth and Marilyn praised the police
OL,18,Ffor bringing Arafiena to justice but
OL,19,Fdecided to try and recoup some of
OL,20,Ftheir money.
