OL,3,CCouple who lost #300k 'nest egg' to
OL,4,Cscam now face bigger bill
OL,6,FPart of the money they had lost,
OL,7,F#160,000, had been paid into an
OL,8,Faccount held by payment service
OL,9,Fprovider Moorwand, but had been
OL,10,Fwithdrawn by the scammers.
OL,12,FThe couple took Moorwand to court
OL,13,Falleging they did not have an adequate
OL,14,Fsystem of checks in place when the
OL,15,Fcompany was set up and so were liable
OL,16,Ffor the losses.
OL,18,FHowever a judge ruled there was no
OL,19,Fbreach of duty of care and the case
OL,20,Fwas dismissed.
