OL,6,FIt means the Hamblins have not only
OL,7,Flost their pension savings but now
OL,8,Fface further legal costs for losing
OL,9,Fthe civil action too.
OL,11,FIn a statement Moorwand said: "The
OL,12,Fjudgement speaks for itself and
OL,13,FMoorwand is truly sorry for the
OL,14,Fpredicament that befell the Hamblins."
OL,16,FFraud prevention groups say scammers
OL,17,Foften target vulnerable people and can
OL,18,Fbe extremely convincing.
