OL,6,FPat Coomber-Wood, CEO Citizens Advice
OL,7,FNorth Oxfordshire, gave this advice to
OL,8,Fanyone looking for investment
OL,9,Fopportunities.
OL,11,FShe said: "Don't be rushed, do your
OL,12,Fhomework and remember if it sounds too
OL,13,Fgood to be true it probably is, so act
OL,14,Fmuch more cautiously, and the other
OL,15,Fkey things are, be really careful
OL,16,Fabout giving away bank details.
OL,18,F"Do all of your due diligence and make
OL,19,Fsure you are not giving away bank
OL,20,Fdetails to an organisation you haven't
OL,21,Fchecked up on."
